><span>注册资本：壹佰玖拾捌万元整<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>法人代表：刘皓<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>股东：刘皓、周家发、李毅、张林、陆盛麟、无锡国联浚源创业投资中心（有限合伙）<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>职工人数：<span>104</span>人<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>内部机构设置：生产部、品管部、技术部、总经办、销售部、财务部、研发部<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>主要经营范围：氟硅弹性体的研发、生产和销售。企业自营产品的进出口业务。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.85pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>本公司是一家专业从事特种合成橡胶材料和具有特殊功能，高附加值的特种高分子材料的研发及相关产品生产、销售与服务一体的高科技企业。公司开发出多种规格型号的氟预混炼胶、氟混炼胶、特种氟混炼胶、全氟醚混炼胶、硅混炼胶、含氟表面活性剂和全氟聚醚油系列高科技产品，填补了多项国内空白，为我国的汽车行业、新能源产业、半导体、航空航天和国防事业做出了卓越贡献。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>公司主要发展历程：<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">(1)2004</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">年<span>10</span>月晨光博达在成都双流蛟龙工业港成立。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">(2)2005</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">年晨光博达通过<span>ISO9001:2000</span>质量管理体系认证、企业自营进出口经营权。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">(3)2006</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">年与国外重大客户签订了出口合同<span>,</span>公司的销售和发展迈入了一个新的台阶。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">(4)2007</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">年晨光博达总经理刘皓被双流县人民政府评为\r\n“优秀企业经营者”。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">(5)2007</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">年晨光博达与中国最大的密封件企业中鼎股份建立长期合作关系，被评为《合格供应商》<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">(6)2008</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">年晨光博达被评为双流县外贸出口“先进企业”<span>,</span>纳税额“先进企业”。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>7</span>）<span>2008</span>年<span>3</span>月晨光博达与世界第一大密封件企业法国哈金森建立长期合作关系。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>8</span>）<span>2009</span>年晨光博达通过国家级“高新技术企业”认证<span>;</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>9</span>）<span>2009</span>年晨光博达被四川省中小企业局、四川省工商业联合会评为“四川省成长型中小企业”<span>,</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>10</span>）<span>2009</span>年晨光博达被双流县金融工作办公室、双流县信用促进会评为“讲诚信 守信用”企业<span>,</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:6pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">(11)2009</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">年晨光博达被中共双流县东升街道工作委员会、双流县人民政府东升街道办事处评为“纳税额先进企业”<span>;</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>12</span>）<span>2009</span>年晨光博达被中国重汽<span>(</span>香港<span>)</span>有限公司评为《合格供应商》；<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:6pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">(13)2010</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">年<span>1</span>月晨光博达成为《中国摩擦密封材料协会》的会员单位。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>14</span>）<span>2010</span>年<span>1</span>月晨光博达成为《中国塑料加工工业协会氟塑料加工专业委员会》的会员单位。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>15</span>）<span>2010</span>年<span>1</span>月晨光博达被双流县金融工作办公室、双流县信用促进会评为“<span>2009</span>年度讲诚信、守信用企业”；<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>16</span>）<span>2010</span>年<span>3</span>月晨光博达被中共双流县东升街道工作委员会、双流县人民政府东升街道办事处评为“<span>2009</span>年度纳税额先进企业”；<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>17</span>）<span>2010</span>年<span>7</span>月晨光博达正在进行的新型汽车发动机密封用氟弹性体的产业化项目被四川省经济和信息化委员会评为“<span>2010</span>年度四川省重点技术创新项目”。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>18</span>）<span>2011</span>年<span>1</span>月晨光博达成为双流县企业信用促进会“理事单位“。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（19）<span>2011</span>年<span>3</span>月晨光博达被中共双流县东升街道工作委员会、双流县人民政府东升街道办事处评为“<span>2010</span>年度提效增速先进企业“。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>20</span>）<span>2011</span>年<span>5</span>月<span>16</span>日，航空港新工厂正式开工。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>21</span>）<span>2011</span>年<span>5</span>月<span>26</span>日公司“博达之家”俱乐部正式成立。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>22</span>）<span>2011</span>年<span>6</span>月<span>1</span>日公司“博文汇”内刊正式成立。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>23</span>）<span>2011</span>年<span>6</span>月<span>6</span>日晨光博达、博达爱福与战略投资者无锡国联俊源投资中心（有限合伙）正式签署投资框架协议。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>  (24)2011<span><span>年6</span></span><span><span>月30</span></span><span><span>日</span></span><span>无锡国联俊源投资中心（有限合伙）注入投资资金，投资合作正式开始。</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>25</span>）<span>2011</span>年<span>12</span>月公司被列入四川省“十二五”规划重点培育和发展的重点新兴战略新材料企业<span></span></span></span><span> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span></span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>26</span>）<span>2012</span>年<span>1</span>月博达新厂竣工开业。<span></span></span></span><span> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span></span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（<span>27</span>）<span>2012</span>年<span>6</span>月成都晨光博达橡塑有限公司经成都市经济和信息化委员会批准成立“市级企业技术中心”。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（28</span>）<span>2012</span>年被复旦安永评选为</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">中国最具潜力企业“<span>37</span>家之一<span></span></span></span><span> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span></span><span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">（29）<span>2012</span>年<span>6</span>月成都晨光博达橡塑有限公司被评为新材料企业。<span></span></span></span><span> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span></span><span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">（<span>30</span>）<span>2013</span>年<span>12</span>月晨光博达取得国家级高新技术企业证书。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">（<span>31</span>）<span>2014</span>年，“高性能注射级氟橡胶项目”通过四川省科技厅成果鉴定为</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">国际先进</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">同年，项目被评为成都市科技进步三等奖。<span></span></span></span><span> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span></span><span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">（<span>32</span>）<span>2014</span>年晨光博达被评定为“成都市知识产权试点企业”。<span></span></span></span><span> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span></span><span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">（<span>33</span>）<span>2015</span>年晨光博达被评为双流县知识产权试点企业，“高性能注射级氟橡胶项目”被评为双流县科技进步二等奖。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span><span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>（34</span>）<span>2015</span>年<span>12</span>月“高性能注射级氟橡胶项目”被评为四川省科技进步三等奖。<span></span></span></span><span> </span>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:12pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span> </span><span> </span></span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">公司成立以来，以“诚信、创新、追求卓越”为经营目标，制定了一套科学严谨的企业管理制度，<span>2005</span>年通过了<span>ISO9001</span>：<span>2000</span>质量体系认证，<span>2009</span>年被评为国家级高新技术企业，实现了稳步健康发展。公司不仅注重国外市场的开拓，同时在大力开拓国内市场，公司产品出口、内销各分别占<span>40%</span>、<span>60%</span>。<span style=\"color:red;\"></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:27.85pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>截止<span>2015</span>年<span>12</span>月，公司共有员工<span>102</span>人，其中大专以上学历人员<span>48</span>人，研究与开发人员<span>29</span>人，中高级职称<span>16</span>人，博士<span>2</span>人，硕士<span>3</span>人。公司拥有一支高素质的科研、管理队伍，其主要成员来自于四川学术界学科带头人，有机氟有机硅行业知名专家、教授及经营管理骨干，长期从事氟硅新材料的生产经营管理和科技研发工作，积累了丰富的管理知识和经验，为企业的持续发展提供了坚实基础。公司坚持科技成果转化工作。近三年来，公司通过独占许可方式获得<span>1</span>项国家授权发明专利，取得发明专利证书<span>5</span>项，实用新型专利证书<span>8</span>项，新申请发明专利<span>9</span>项。成功实现了二十多项科技成果转化，年均转化数达<span>5</span>项，取得了良好的经济效益和社会效益。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.85pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>公司坚持自主创新，建立完善的研发管理体系，具有良好的研发基础条件。公司制定了科技项目管理制度，严格执行项目立项报告和审批程序；建立了研发投入核算体系和科技奖励考核机制；设立产品技术研发中心，并配备先进的研发设施设备；进一步提升新型特种橡胶混炼技术水平及产品产业化升级，增强企业核心竞争力。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.85pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>公司通过技术创新，不断优化产品和改善服务，取得对外贸易经营权，产品畅销国内外，实现了科技与效益的快速增长。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>“诚信是企业之本，创新是企业之源，追求卓越是永远的目标”晨光博达秉持这一信念，“见微知博，达闻天下”不断拓展氟硅高端产业各项业务，扎根本土，放眼世界，努力将公司建成与国际化大企业产品相配套的具有全球化视野的国际型、创新型企业。<span class=\"apple-style-span\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\"> </span></span><span style=\"color:#C00000;\"></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.85pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>   </span><span>                                 </span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">成都晨光博达橡塑有限公司<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"right\">\r\n	<span> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.85pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"><span>  </span><span>                                        </span>2015</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">年<span>12</span>月3<span>1</span>日<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>', null, null, null, null, '0.00', '0.00', null, null, '0', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null);
